    "data": "بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْم\nبِسْمِ اللهِ كَلِمَةِ الْمُعْتَصِمِيْنَ وَ مَقَالَةِ الْمُتَحَرِّزِيْنَ وَ اَعُوْذُ بِاللهِ تَعَالٰى مِنْ جَوْرِ الْجَآئِرِيْنَ وَ كَيْدِ الْحَاسِدِيْنَ وَ بَغْـىِ الظَّالِمِيْنَ وَ اَحْمَدُهٗ فَوْقَ حَمْدِ الْحَامِدِيْنَ اَللّٰهُمَّ اَنْتَ الْوَاحِدُ بِلاَ شَرِيْكٍ وَالْمَلِكُ بِلاَ تَمْلِيْكٍ لَا تُضَادُّ فِىْ حُكْمِكَ وَ لَا تُنَازَعُ فِىْ مُلْكِكَ اَسْئَلُكَ اَنْ تُصَلِّىَ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ عَبْدِكَ وَ رَسُوْلِكَ وَ اَنْ تُوْزِعَنِىْ مِنْ شُكْرِ نُعْمَاكَ مَا تَبْلُغُ بِىْ غَايَةَ رِضَاكَ وَ اَنْ تُعِيْنَنِىْ عَلٰى طَاعَتِكَ وَ لُزُوْمِ عِبَادَتِكَ وَاسْتِحْقَاقِ مَثُوْبَتِكَ بِلُطْفِ عِنَايَتِكَ وَ تَرْحَمَنِىْ بِصَدِّىْ عَنْ مَعَاصِيْكَ مَا اَحْيَيْتَنِىْ وَ تُوَفِّقَنِىْ لِمَا يَنْفَعُنِىْ مَا اَبْقَيْتَنِىْ وَ اَنْ تَشْرَحَ بِكِتَابِكَ صَدْرِىْ وَ تَحُطَّ بِتِلاَوَتِهٖ وِزْرِىْ وَ تَمْنَحَنِىْ السَّلاَمَةَ فِىْ دِيْنِىْ وَ نَفْسِىْ وَلاَ تُوحِشَ بِىْ اَهْلَ اُنْسِىْ وَ تُتِمَّ اِحْسَانَكَ فِيْمَا بَقِىَ مِنْ عُمْرِىْ كَمَا اَحْسَنْتَ فِيْمَا مَضٰى مِنْهُ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ.\nBISMIL LAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM\nBISMIL LAAHE KALEMATUL MOA’TASEMEENA WA MAQAALATUL MOTAHARREZEENA WA A-O’OZO BILLAHE TA-A’ALA MIN JAWRIL JAA-EREENA WA KAYDIL HAASEDEENA WA BAGHYIZ ZAALEMEENAWA AHMADOHU FAWQA HAMDIL HAAMEDEENA ALLAAHUMMA ANTAL WAAHEDO BELAA SHAREEKIN WAL MALEKO BELAA TAMLEEKIN LAA TOZAADDO FEE HUKMEKA WA LAA TONAAZA-O’ FEE MULKEKA ASALOKA AN TOSALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN A’BDEKA WA RASOOLEKA WA AN TOOZE-ANEE MIN SHUKRE NOA’MAAKA MAA TABLOGHO BEE GHAAYATA REZAAKA WA AN TO-E’ENANEE A’LAA TAA-ATEKA WA LUZOOME E’BAADATEKA WAS-TEHQAAQE MASOOBATEKA BE LUTFE E’NAAYATEKA WA TARHAMANEE BE SADDEE A’N MA-A’ASEEKA MAA AHYAYTANEE WA TOWAFFIQNEE LEMAA YANFA-O’NEE MAA ABQAYTANEE WA AN TASHRAHA BE KITAABEKA SADREE WA TA-HUTTA BE-TELAAWATEHI WIZREE WA TAMNA-HANIS SALAAMATA FEE DEENEE WA NAFSEE WA LAA TOO-HESHA BEE AHLA UNSEE WA TOTIMMA EHSAANAKA FEEMA BAQEYA MIN U’MREE KAMAA AHSANTA FEEMAA MAZAA MINHO YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEEN.\n‘In the name of Allah’, the word of those who hold fast to Him, the speech of those who seek His protection! I seek refuge in Allah (high exalted is He) from the injustice of the unjust, the trickery of the enviers, and the oppression of the wrongdoers, and I praise Him beyond the praise of the praisers! O Allah, Youare the One without partner, and the King without having been made sovereign; no one opposes You in Your decree and no one contests You in Your kingdom! I ask You to bless Muhammad and his Household, Your servant and Your messenger, inspire me with a thanksgiving for Your favours which will take me to the utmost limit of Your good pleasure, help me through the gentleness of Your solitude to obey You, hold fast to worshipping You, and deserve Your reward, have mercy upon me, bar me from acts of disobedience toward You as long as You keepest me alive, give me success in what profits me as long as You sparest me, expand my breast through Your Book, lessen my burden through its recitation, bestow upon me health in my religion and my soul, estrange not my intimates from me, and complete Your beneficence in what is left of my lifetime, just as Youhave shown beneficence in that of it which has passed! O Most Merciful of the merciful!", 
    "title": "The Supplication of Saturday"
}